      • create

        public String create()
        Returns:
        new page
        Throws:
        org.egov.infra.validation.exception.ValidationException -
        The details of transaction is
        1. addToIntrument- cheque information
        2. createVoucher- JV creation
        3. update instrument -link jv and cheque
        4. addTocontraJournalVoucher
        5. post to ledger

      • edit

        public String edit()
        Returns:
        edit page
        Modifies the Bank to Bank Transfer ContraVoucher .       Details of transaction:
        1. update the VoucherHeader for all mis attribute changes
        2. If Account Numbers changed
          1. cancel the Instrument
          2. create new Instrument
          3. delete ledger
          4. recreate Ledger
        3. If only instrument date and amount is changed update only instrument
